ewart and Gustav Robert Kirchhoff: two independent approaches to \"Kirchhoff's radiation law\"\n |journal=[[Isis (journal)|Isis]]\n |volume=67 |issue=4\n |pages=565\u2013600\n |doi=10.1086/351669\n |pmid=794025\n |ref=harv\n}}\n*{{cite journal\n |last1=Stewart |first1=B.\n |author1-link=Balfour Stewart\n |year=1858\n |title=An account of some experiments on radiant heat\n |journal=[[Transactions of the Royal Society of Edinburgh]]\n |volume=22 |pages=1\u201320\n |url=https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=mdp.39015005551075;view=1up;seq=165\n |doi=10.1017/S0080456800031288\n |ref=harv\n}}\n*{{cite journal\n |last1=Wien |first1=W.\n |author1-link=Wilhelm Wien\n |year=1894\n |title=Temperatur und Entropie der Strahlung\n |trans-title=Temperature and entropy of radiation\n |journal=[[Annalen der Physik]]\n |volume=288 |issue=5\n |pages=132\u2013165\n |url=https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=wu.89048352843;view=1up;seq=148\n |doi= 10.1002/andp.18942880511\n |ref=harv\n|bibcode = 1894AnP...288..132W }}\n{{refend}}\n\n==Further reading==\n\n*{{cite book|author1=Kroemer, Herbert |author2=Kittel, Charles |title=Thermal Physics |edition=2nd|publisher=W. H. Freeman Company|year=1980\n|isbn=0-7167-1088-9}}\n*{{cite book|author1=Tipler, Paul |author2=Llewellyn, Ralph |title=Modern Physics |edition=4th|publisher=W. H. Freeman|year=2002|isbn=0-7167-4345-0}}\n<!--\n{{cite journal\n|journal = The Academy\n|title = Science: Draper's Memoirs\n|volume = XIV\n|issue = 338\n|publisher = London: Robert Scott Walker\n|date = Oct 26, 1878\n|page = 408\n|url = https://archive.org/details/scientificmemoi00drapgoog\n}}\n-->\n\n==External links==\n*[http://iwant2study.org/ospsg/index.php//605 Black-body radiation JavaScript Interactives] Black-body radiation by Fu-Kwun Hwang and Loo Kang Wee\n*[http://www.spectralcalc.com/blackbody/blackbody.html Calculating Black-body Radiation] Interactive calculator with Doppler Effect. Includes most systems of units.\n*[http://academo.org/demos/colour-t